{"word":"G4244 - πρεσβυτέριον - presbytérion - pres-boo-ter'-ee-on - Elder","slug":"G4244","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρεσβυτέριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>presbytérion"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pres-boo-ter'-ee-on"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Elder"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x03C3;&#x03B2;&#x03C5;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03BF;&#x03BD; - presbuterion</b> - <i>pres-boo-ter'-ee-on</i><p/>Neuter of a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G4245\">G4245</a>; the <i>order of elders</i>, that is, (specifically) Israelite <i>Sanhedrim</i> or Christian &ldquo;presbytery&rdquo;: - (estate of) elder (-s), presbytery."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4243\">G4243</a>, <a href=\"#/G4245\">G4245</a>, <a href=\"#/G4246\">G4246</a>, <a href=\"#/G4247\">G4247</a>, <a href=\"#/G4850\">G4850</a>"}]}